⚠️ Failure Modes (Important)
	1.	Mode Lock
	•	stuck in Auditor → paralysis
	•	stuck in Explorer → chaos
	2.	Premature Switching
	•	switching before a phase completes
	3.	Wrong Signal Interpretation
	•	misreading state → wrong mode

⸻

🧠 Simple Heuristic (Field Rule)

If you want a fast version:
	•	confused → Explorer
	•	overwhelmed → Strategist
	•	executing → Operator
	•	something feels off → Auditor
	•	nothing happening → Builder

